import numpy as np
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt 
import seaborn as sns

import plotly.graph_objects as go
from sklearn.preprocessing import OneHotEncoder
import warnings
warnings.filterwarnings('ignore')
url = "https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ImriElkouby/Project/main/Israeli%20civilians%20killed%20by%20Palestinians.csv"
terror_df = pd.read_csv(url, encoding="ISO-8859-8")

Data Cleaning and Preprocessing:

terror_df.rename(columns={'Took part in the hostilities': 'Background in terrorism'}, inplace=True)
terror_df['Background in terrorism'] = terror_df['Background in terrorism'].fillna('No')
terror_df['Background in terrorism'] = terror_df['Background in terrorism'].str.replace('Israelis','Yes',regex = False)

terror_df['date_event']=pd.to_datetime(terror_df['Date of event'],format='%m/%d/%Y')
terror_df['date_death']=pd.to_datetime(terror_df['Date of death'],format='%m/%d/%Y')
terror_df['weekday_event'] = pd.DatetimeIndex(terror_df['date_event']).strftime('%A')
terror_df['month_event'] = pd.DatetimeIndex(terror_df['date_event']).month

terror_df['event to death time'] = (terror_df['date_death'] - terror_df['date_event']).dt.days

terror_df[terror_df['date_event']=='2001-05-09']#     ,     1    
terror_df.loc[834,'event to death time']=0

#    2000-2023
ramadan_dates = pd.DataFrame({'year': list(range(2000, 2024)),'ramadan_start':
        ['2000-11-27', '2001-11-16', '2002-11-06', '2003-10-27', '2004-10-16',
        '2005-10-05', '2006-09-24', '2007-09-13', '2008-09-01', '2009-08-22',
        '2010-08-11', '2011-08-01', '2012-07-20', '2013-07-09', '2014-06-29',
        '2015-06-18', '2016-06-06', '2017-05-27', '2018-05-16', '2019-05-06',
        '2020-04-24', '2021-04-13', '2022-04-02', '2023-03-23'],

'ramadan_end': ['2000-12-26', '2001-12-15', '2002-12-05', '2003-11-25', '2004-11-14',
        '2005-11-03', '2006-10-23', '2007-10-12', '2008-09-30', '2009-09-20',
        '2010-09-09', '2011-08-29', '2012-08-18', '2013-08-07', '2014-07-27',
        '2015-07-16', '2016-07-05', '2017-06-24', '2018-06-14', '2019-06-04',
        '2020-05-23', '2021-05-12', '2022-05-01', '2023-04-20']})


#   
ramadan_dates['ramadan_start'] = pd.to_datetime(ramadan_dates['ramadan_start'])
ramadan_dates['ramadan_end'] = pd.to_datetime(ramadan_dates['ramadan_end'])

#       
def is_in_ramadan(row):
    event_date = row['date_event']
    event_year = event_date.year
    ramadan_row = ramadan_dates[ramadan_dates['year'] == event_year]
    if not ramadan_row.empty:
        start = ramadan_row['ramadan_start'].values[0]
        end = ramadan_row['ramadan_end'].values[0]
        return start <= event_date <= end
    else:
        return False  #     
        
terror_df['is_in_ramadan'] = terror_df.apply(is_in_ramadan, axis=1)

terror_df['Type of injury'] = terror_df['Type of injury'].str.replace('physically assaulted', 'physical assault', regex = False)
 #      ,      
terror_df['Event location'] = terror_df['Event location'].replace({'Tel Aviv': 'Tel Aviv-Yafo','Tel Aviv-Yafo-Yafo':'Tel Aviv-Yafo','Old City (Jerusalem)':'Jerusalem','East Jerusalem':'Jerusalem','West Jerusalem':'Jerusalem'})

terror_df['injury_groups'] = terror_df['Type of injury'].replace({'beating': 'physical assault','physical assault': 'physical assault','Strangulation': 'physical assault'})
Type_of_injury_ordered=['stones throwing','physical assault','stabbing','being bludgeoned with an axe','hit by a vehicle','gunfire','explosion']
terror_df['Type_of_injury_coded'] = pd.Categorical(terror_df['injury_groups'], categories=Type_of_injury_ordered,ordered=True).codes
terror_df['Ammunition']=terror_df['Ammunition'].replace({'missile':'rocket','grad rocket':'rocket','Qassam rocket':'rocket','mortar fire':'rocket'})

grouped_incidents_full = terror_df.groupby(['date_event', 'Event location'])\
.agg({'Event location - Region': 'first','Background in terrorism':'first','Citizenship':'first','Ammunition': 'first','Type of injury': lambda x: x.dropna().unique()[0] if len(x.dropna().unique()) > 0 else None,'injury_groups': lambda x: x.dropna().unique()[0] if len(x.dropna().unique()) > 0 else None,'Name':'count','is_in_ramadan':'first'}).reset_index().rename(columns={'Name': 'Victim Count'})

Correlations:

numeric=['Age','date_event','date_death','month_event','event to death time','Type_of_injury_coded']
categorical=['Event location - Region','Gender','Background in terrorism','is_in_ramadan']
all_features=categorical+numeric
terror_df_num = pd.get_dummies(terror_df[all_features])
correlation_matrix=terror_df_num.corr(numeric_only=False, method='spearman').round(2)
plt.figure(figsize=(15,6))
sns.heatmap(data=correlation_matrix,cmap='coolwarm',annot=True)
plt.xticks(rotation=45, ha='right')
plt.show()
